free: #e The child takes a frog, which seems to be the one he raised before.
#c 小孩子就拿了好像是他以前養的那一隻青蛙。
#n qa-qudu-an-na 他(打算)要養的 (Something that) he (intends to) raise.
#n pa-qudu 寄養/使別人養 to have somebody adopt/raise something
#n qudu 有養或照顧的意思, 但如果對象是大眾則用 m-liatip
#n qudu denotes the sense of ‘to raise; to take care of’, but if the object is the 'public' then ‘m-liatip’ must be used.
